### Contact API Test File
### This file contains sample requests to test your contact API
### Use this in VS Code with REST Client extension or any HTTP client

### 1. Health Check - Test if API is working
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/health

### 2. Submit a basic contact inquiry
POST http://localhost:8080/main/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "+91 9876543210",
  "serviceType": "project-assistance",
  "message": "I need help with my final year project on web development.",
  "preferredContactMethod": "email"
}

### 3. Submit an internship inquiry with all details
POST http://localhost:8080/main/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "phone": "+91 9876543211",
  "serviceType": "internship",
  "internshipTrack": "fullstack",
  "duration": "3-months",
  "experienceLevel": "beginner",
  "message": "I want to learn full-stack development through internship.",
  "preferredContactMethod": "phone-call",
  "preferredDate": "2024-01-15",
  "preferredTime": "10:00 AM"
}

### 4. Submit a custom project idea inquiry
POST http://localhost:8080/main/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mike Johnson",
  "email": "mike.johnson@example.com",
  "phone": "+91 9876543212",
  "serviceType": "internship",
  "internshipTrack": "custom",
  "duration": "6-months",
  "experienceLevel": "intermediate",
  "customIdea": "I want to build an AI-powered e-commerce recommendation system using machine learning and web technologies.",
  "message": "I have a specific project idea and need guidance on implementation.",
  "preferredContactMethod": "whatsapp"
}

### 5. Get all contact inquiries (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/all

### 6. Get contact inquiry by ID (replace 1 with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/1

### 7. Get contact inquiries by email
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/email/john.doe@example.com

### 8. Get contact inquiries by service type
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/service/internship

### 9. Get contact inquiries by status
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/status/NEW

### 10. Get recent contact inquiries (last 30 days)
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/recent

### 11. Update contact status (replace 1 with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/main/contact/1/status?status=CONTACTED

### 12. Get contact statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/main/contact/statistics
